flowchart LR
    user[Usuario]
    dashboard[Frontend Dashboard\nVite + React]
    gateway[API Gateway\nFastAPI]
    db[(PostgreSQL)]
    rabbit[(RabbitMQ)]
    keymgr[Key Manager\nFastAPI]
    ocr[OCR Service\nOpenRouter OCR]
    llm[LLM Service\nOpenRouter JSON]
    ftpapi[FTP API\nFastAPI]
    ftp[(FTP Server)]
    openrouter[OpenRouter\nModelos OCR + LLM]

    user --> dashboard
    dashboard -->|HTTP| gateway

    gateway -->|CRUD documentos\nlogs\nresultados| db
    gateway -->|consulta / gestion de claves| keymgr
    gateway -->|subida / visualizacion\nde archivos| ftpapi
    ftpapi --> ftp

    gateway -->|enqueue document_uploaded| rabbit
    rabbit -->|document_uploaded| ocr

    ocr -->|descarga archivo| ftpapi
    ocr -->|obtiene API keys activas| keymgr
    ocr -->|OCR PDF / imagen| openrouter
    ocr -->|ocr_complete| rabbit
    ocr -->|text_extracted| rabbit
    ocr -->|processing_failed| rabbit

    rabbit -->|text_extracted| llm
    llm -->|obtiene API keys activas| keymgr
    llm -->|normalizacion a JSON| openrouter
    llm -->|processing_complete| rabbit
    llm -->|processing_failed| rabbit

    rabbit -->|ocr_complete| gateway
    rabbit -->|processing_complete| gateway
    rabbit -->|processing_failed| gateway

    gateway -->|persistencia final\nraw_text + json_result + metadatos| db
    gateway -->|archivo original / detalle| dashboard

    classDef storage fill:#eef6ff,stroke:#2b6cb0,color:#1a365d;
    classDef service fill:#f7fafc,stroke:#4a5568,color:#1a202c;
    classDef external fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#c05621,color:#7b341e;
    classDef queue fill:#f0fff4,stroke:#2f855a,color:#22543d;

    class db,ftp storage;
    class gateway,keymgr,ocr,llm,ftpapi,dashboard service;
    class rabbit queue;
    class user,openrouter external;
